data.description: Upgraded, waterfront 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with many upgrades including metal roof, HardiePlank siding, impact windows, granite countertops, LVT flooring and A/C.  Open concept floorpan with kitchen island, dining room, family room and double sliding glass doors with access to your 192 Sqft screened/covered back porch overlooking the water.  2 large bedrooms, guest bathroom, master bathroom en-suite and full-size laundry room.  Crown molding, white shaker style kitchen cabinets, 60'x4' concrete dock, covered parking, over 500 Sqft of storage and large yard with plenty of room for your Boat, RV, trailers and toys!  Great boating access to Cudjoe Bay, Ocean and Gulf just minutes from the amazing crystal clear waters of the Florida Keys destinations like Content Keys, Snipe Key, Tarpon Belly and many more with our famous fishing, diving, snorkeling and kayak/paddle boarding.  This home is just 25 minutes to Key West with shopping, night life, water sports and much more.  Enjoy the walking/bike path in the neighborhood or go to Big Pine Park or Bahia Honda State Park to enjoy time with friends and family.  Local grocery store, convenience stores and much more within a mile of your new home!This house is in a sought after neighborhood in Cudjoe Key, centrally located between Key West and Marathon with access to all the Keys have to offer.  Possible assumption of current VA loan balance to qualified buyers with an interest rate under 3%!  Come take a look and make Cudjoe Key and the Florida Keys your new home.  Very easy to show!  Seller is motivated!
